{"tid":1496001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"恥夾：「14億人的意志可以組織和操控嗎？」","createTime":"2019-08-22T10:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T11:34:15.000Z","uid":73381,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"acf81471e0d3a6961f701e962549ef1333c4247c","tid":1496001,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"中國外交部22日下午舉行例行記者會，外媒提問時引述分析指出，是中國駐外機構在背後組織這些海外中國公民上街。<br />\n<br />\n對此，耿爽表示，「包括香港同胞在內的14億中國人民，對香港局勢最大的訴求就是止暴制亂、恢復秩序，最大期待就是恢復香港繁榮穩定，這是14億中國人共同的意志，你覺得14億人的意志是可以組織和操控起來的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n他說，這些海外中國公民對「妄圖分裂國家、抹黑中國形象的言行表示憤慨、反對，完全理所應該，也是情理當中的事」，但希望海外中國公民能「理性表達愛國熱情，注意保護自身安全」。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽還說，中國政府一貫要求海外中國公民遵守當地法律法規，也希望有國家尊重理解海外中國公民合法活動，保障維護他們的合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4004205\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5603%2F4004205&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2La3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=4820425b\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5603/4004205</a>"},{"pid":"949a44ef7f021817ea26ce1df01d69b7159b81e4","tid":1496001,"uid":73381,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"恥夾講真話👍🏼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6703d9ad2a538767f1a84dff4f420766a8eaf8c1","tid":1496001,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:03:08.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"56b90afa543b4d0e112938a00947efaf2047f53c","tid":1496001,"uid":101606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"講緊共匪？"},{"pid":"dea6e0918fe8f7f8dc001fea3446b729a9725c1d","tid":1496001,"uid":48667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"支共可以"},{"pid":"9c0c00f7c6bfe6228fc3d4dc82eff43976cae14a","tid":1496001,"uid":34970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T10:06:24.0